*xawdecode-1.8.2 (21 Jan 2004)

  21 Jan 2004; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.8.0.ebuild,
  xawdecode-1.8.1.ebuild, xawdecode-1.8.2.ebuild,
  files/xawdecode-1.8.2-configure-alsa-fixes.patch:
  version bump, and switched to use_enable syntax instead. This closes bug
  #34766 by dju` <dju@elegiac.net>, with ebuilds and patches provided by: TGL
  <degrenier@easyconnect.fr>

*xawdecode-1.8.1 (06 Nov 2003)

  06 Nov 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.8.1.ebuild:
  version bump thanks to: TGL <degrenier@easyconnect.fr> in bug #30438

  28 Oct 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.6.8.ebuild,
  xawdecode-1.7.5_beta.ebuild, xawdecode-1.8.0.ebuild:
  due to lack of bugs on x86 and ppc for xawdecode, pushing 1.8.0 to stable

  26 Sep 2003; Michael Sterrett <msterret@gentoo.org>
  xawdecode-1.7.5_beta.ebuild, xawdecode-1.8.0.ebuild:
  x11-libs/xaw -> x11-libs/Xaw3d

*xawdecode-1.8.0 (14 Sep 2003)

  14 Sep 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.8.0.ebuild:
  version bump thanks to: TGL <degrenier@easyconnect.fr> in bug #28658

*xawdecode-1.7.5_beta (12 Sep 2003)

  12 Sep 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  xawdecode-1.7.5_beta.ebuild:
  Version bump thanks to: Christian Loitsch <gentoo-bug@loitsch.org>. Many
  fix-ups were made to Christian's submitted ebuild, which are in this ebuild
  now. Those were made by: TGL <degrenier@easyconnect.fr> in bug #27145

  18 Jun 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.6.7.ebuild,
  xawdecode-1.6.8.ebuild:
  move to stable

*xawdecode-1.6.7 (18 Jun 2003)

  18 Jun 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.6.7.ebuild,
  xawdecode-1.6.8.ebuild:
  moved to media-tv

*xawdecode-1.6.8 (18 May 2003)

  18 May 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> xawdecode-1.6.8.ebuild:
